parameters.name: Description
parameters.value:
To check the  NSTP flow for  Issue Proposal  for Family Floater  Policy when trigger to UWR bucket when  proposed insured person/s  Questionarrie.
Policy Plan Family Floater
Business Type New Business
Members :3A
employee discount : yes
Member Age M1: 35Y
Member Age M2: 23Y
Member Age M3: 22Y
SI : 500000
Questionarrier: 1.1. Do you suffer from any pre-existing illness? Yes/ No

Member 1:Arthritis-Accept
Member 2:Gout-Accept with PED
Member 3:Vericose veins-Accept with PED and loading(10%)

Level 1:OPS
Level 2:UWR
    M1 : Cronic Disease - No, Source PED: Proporsal form, waiting period - 0
    M2 : Cronic Disease - Yes, Source PED: Proporsal form, waiting period - 12
    M3 : Cronic Disease - No, Source PED: Proporsal form, waiting period - 24, Loading %  - 10
Level 3:COL-OPS
Collection Mode = Cheque

Ops->Refer to UWR-> Accept; Accept with PED; Accept with PED and loading-> COL->OPS-> COL Accept-> Loading Payment-> Policy Issuance
